name: Running Dot
description: Hello! One more Interactive art from 0psibC. At this time, a cursor will run for ever in the screen when you press space or touch somewhere you'll draw a line (or a dot if the cursor is very very fast) on it! Have some effects as well! Obs: For brazilian people - there is a message from 0psib to you inside the game. If you like it, take a screenshot and share with me on twitter: @OpsibC!
